ementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-framed .elementor-drop-cap{color:#69727d;border:3px solid;background-color:transparent}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap{margin-top:8px}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap-letter{width:1em;height:1em}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap{float:left;text-align:center;line-height:1;font-size:50px}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap-letter{display:inline-block}<\/style>\t\t\t\t<div>\n<p>Emobella Engineering Nigeria Limited is an indigenous mechanical and electrical engineering service company with core competency in Metal Fabrication, Pipe Fitting and Welding, Instrumentation and Control, Pressure Vessel Inspection, Safety Valve Testing and Certification and Plant Equipment Installation. We are a full-fledged professional engineering company located in the heart of Lagos State to provide services that meet all our clients&#8217; engineering service need at the same time, providing quality services while minimizing cost for our clients without compromising safety.<\/p>\n<p><\/p>\n<p><strong>Our Company History&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Emobella Engineering Nigeria Limited was founded in March 13, 2012 and incorporated under the laws of the Federal Republic of Nigeria to address challenging issues in the engineering industry and also provide quality services while reducing costs.<\/p>\n<p>Emobella Engineering Nigeria Limited is an indigenous mechanical and electrical company specialized in Safety Valve Testing &amp; Certification, Plant Equipment Installation, Pipe Fitting and Welding, Metal Fabrication, Thermal Insulation and Duct Work, Pressure Vessel Inspection, Installation of Fire Detection, Fire Alarm and FM 200 System, Instrumentation and Control, Sales of Pumps, Flow Meter, Pressure Gauge, Pressure Transmitter, Gas Regulator and Thermowell.<\/p>\n<p>Emobella\u2019s primary focus is to provide products and services which will enable clients operate more efficiently, safely and profitably. We are indeed committed to providing solutions that will continuously meet and surpass the expectations of our esteemed clients.<\/p>\n<p>Emobella\u2019s guiding corporate philosophy encompasses high quality services, unparalleled service innovations and competitive pricing. Our team comprised of experienced personnel that has the sole purpose of delivering one stop shop cost effective and quality services.<\/p>\n<p><\/p>\n<p><strong>Our Philosophy<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>&nbsp;<\/strong>We are globally aware and locally sensitive, sharing our expertise and experience to create innovative solutions, making us solution partners in support of our clients.<\/p>\n<p><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><b>Health and Safety Policy Statement<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Emobella Engineering Nigeria Limited is committed to the health and safety of its employees&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">and all who are involved in the delivery of projects, products, and services. Protection of&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">employees from work-related injuries or occupational disease is a major objective at&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">Emobella. Therefore, the management of the company promises that every precaution in all&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">circumstances will be taken for the protection of all our employees and others who may be&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">affected by our work. No job is to be regarded as urgent at the expense of safety.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">At Emobella Engineering Nigeria Limited, we are committed to:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Maintaining and continually improving the Occupational Health and Safety Management&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">System to eliminate hazards and reduce health &amp; safety risks to all our employees and&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">other relevant interested parties.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li>Fulfilling and, where possible, exceeding all applicable health &amp; safety legal and other&nbsp;<span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">requirements<\/span><\/li>\n<li>Integrating health &amp; safety procedures and best practices into every operational activity&nbsp;<span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">with assigned line-functional responsibilities at all levels.<\/span><\/li>\n<li>Involving our employees and other relevant interested parties in maintaining a safe and&nbsp;<span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">healthy work environment through consultation and participation<\/span><\/li>\n<li>Inculcating a safety culture by visible leadership and management commitment<\/li>\n<li>Ensuring required competency to enable our employees work safely.<\/li>\n<li>Setting health and safety objectives as indicators of excellence, monitoring progress and&nbsp;<span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">continually improving health and safety performance.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">Although the Managing Director has ultimate responsibility for health and safety, all&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">employees of Emobella Engineering Nigeria Limited also have the responsibility of ensuring the&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">successful implementation and maintenance of this policy.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\"><br><\/span><\/p>\n<p><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><b>Quality Policy Statement<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Emobella Engineering Nigeria Limited is committed to providing excellent mechanical and&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">electrical engineering products and services that consistently satisfies the requirements of&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">our customers in the Construction, Food &amp; Beverage, and Oil and Gas industries.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Policy Objective<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Quality is important to our business because we value our customers and we strive to provide&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">our customers with products and services which meet and exceed their expectations.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">We are committed to continual improvement and to meeting all legal and other applicable&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">requirements and as such have established a Quality Management System that meets the&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">requirements of the ISO 9001:2015 standard, which provides a framework for benchmarking,&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">measuring and improving our services and performance.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">We have the following systems and procedures in place to support us in our aim of providing&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">quality goods and services, total customer satisfaction and continuous improvement&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">throughout our business:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">Gathering and monitoring of customer feedback&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">A<\/span>&nbsp;customer complaints procedure&nbsp;<\/li>\n<li>Selection and performance monitoring of suppliers against set criteria&nbsp;<\/li>\n<li>Training and development for our employees&nbsp;<\/li>\n<li>Regular audit of our internal processes&nbsp;<\/li>\n<li>Measurable quality objectives which reflect our business aims&nbsp;<\/li>\n<li>Management reviews of audit results, customer feedback and complaints<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">This policy sets the framework for the establishment and review of our quality objectives.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Although the Managing Director has ultimate responsibility for Quality, all employees of&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">Emobella Engineering Nigeria Limited also have the responsibility of ensuring the successful&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">implementation and maintenance of this policy.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-iq94r4k elementor-section-content-middle elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"iq94r4k\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-c74b982\" data-id=\"c74b982\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element element